{"tid":633334,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"今年碩士畢業 fit爆陳法拉返港拍廣告晒美腿","createTime":"2018-04-18T08:23:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T00:53:45.000Z","uid":28366,"like":481,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"48da5472a447ab58a9a510dfd0883148615b6a74","tid":633334,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T08:23:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2018/04/20180417_EN_Fala_Chan_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2018%2F04%2F20180417_EN_Fala_Chan_1.jpg&h=c067b2b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">陳法拉重返校園讚生活規律，本月上演畢業習作後將再次投入演藝工作。</span><br />\n<br />\n陳法拉為修身品牌擔任第二年代言人，日前從美國返港拍廣告，問到法拉何時是身形最Sharp的狀態？她自覺身體最健康的時候狀態就最好，「例如在2014年重返校園，到紐約修讀為期4年的戲劇碩士課程，由全職演員變成全職學生，要上課及排戲，雖然學生生活依舊忙碌，但比過往變得更規律，而且運動量足夠。即將在今年完成碩士課程的法拉，4月便會上演畢業習作，並再次投入演藝工作。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2018/04/20180417_EN_Fala_Chan_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2018%2F04%2F20180417_EN_Fala_Chan_2.jpg&h=4ee8b55a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2018/04/20180417_EN_Fala_Chan.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2018%2F04%2F20180417_EN_Fala_Chan.jpg&h=50b03db1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拍攝當天氣溫只得13度，剛返港的法拉隨即展開工作，拍攝團隊準備充足，為法拉準備了3部暖爐和大量暖包，以免穿上短裙短褲拍攝的法拉受寒風影響。法拉在拍攝前又做足拉筋熱身，務求把每個動作做得盡善盡美。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2018/04/20180417_EN_Fala_Chan_3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2018%2F04%2F20180417_EN_Fala_Chan_3.jpg&h=8242b5c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/3016850-今年碩士畢業-陳法拉返港拍廣告騷長腿\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F3016850-%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E7%A2%A9%E5%A3%AB%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD-%E9%99%B3%E6%B3%95%E6%8B%89%E8%BF%94%E6%B8%AF%E6%8B%8D%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A%E9%A8%B7%E9%95%B7%E8%85%BF&d=tqRGKOaiWHhoCo5CzJ7%2BztibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=4f50f9e6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/3016850-今年碩士畢業-陳法拉返港拍廣告騷長腿</a>"},{"pid":"8101176362893316cc9328e3917450a33f8f51f5","tid":633334,"uid":28366,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T08:30:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f1d06474fd6cb542c9206225bdfb03f4ebb5d21","tid":633334,"uid":108993,"like":139,"dislike":2,"score":137,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T08:31:03.000Z","msg":"越老越正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"245b83d1d00faa991eea39fb006552b183bcbdc6","tid":633334,"uid":157362,"like":251,"dislike":3,"score":248,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T08:32:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab384144b71cb010e293d3df6ac7acb299fd84f6","tid":633334,"uid":23833,"like":249,"dislike":14,"score":235,"quote":{"pid":"245b83d1d00faa991eea39fb006552b183bcbdc6","tid":633334,"uid":157362,"like":251,"dislike":3,"score":248,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T08:32:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T08:34:12.000Z","msg":"一睇就知佢係乜鳩都管果類女人啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一個男人大把錢<br />\n<br />\n都比心管成咁<br />\n<br />\n係你都走囉"},{"pid":"c14c22243dd05f6584469ef2b73a1cfacd40633f","tid":633334,"uid":101976,"like":91,"dislike":4,"score":87,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T08:46:35.000Z","msg":"笑得靚既人真係好屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm